Kathryn Card https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kathryn_Card 0 Kathryn Card (October 4, 1892 – March 1, 1964) was an American radio, television and film actress who may be best remembered for her role as Mrs. MacGillicuddy, Lucy's mother on I Love Lucy.
